Package: knx-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: dialog, initrd-tools, perl, bash (>>2.05), lilo, kdm, (grub-gfxboot (>>0.95-4) | grub (>>0.95)), (kudzu-kanotix | kudzu-knoppix | kudzu), whois, yaird, initscripts-kanotix, ifrename
Suggests: qtparted, xdialog, fix-cdrom, distro-defaults
Description: installs kanotix to hd
 kanotix-installer is an fully functional installation program
 to easily install kanotix to hd. It has support for config-files, 
 which allow more advanced usages.

